SocketApplication.class/ESA_Application_MaxSockets

   NAME
        ESA_Application_MaxSockets -- (V1 ) [I..], LONG

   FUNCTION
        Set maximum number of available sockets for this application.  When
        the maximum is reached then all subsequent ESM_Socket_Open calls will
        fail until one or more sockets are closed.

        Default is 64 sockets.

   SEE ALSO
        bsdsocket.library/SocketBaseTagList()

